        <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl shadow-lg p-8 transform hover:scale-[1.02] transition-transform duration-300 border border-green-100">
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-4 text-black">When We Visited & What the Weather was Like</h3>
          <p class="text-black">We travelled to Dubai in the mid of October for 11 days and the weather was a bit hot in the afternoons. The weather in the mornings and evening was nice and pleasant. For us the most incredible part was going around the city like a local. We always opted for metros / buses over cabs and that really made us feel like a part of the city.</p>
